text: No Stars in the Jungle () is a 1967 Peruvian Argentine adventure movie directed by Armando Robles Godoy and starring Ignacio Quirós, Susana Pardahl, Luisa Otero, Jorge Montoro, Jorge Aragón. ==Other websites== * Category:1967 adventure movies Category:Peruvian movies Category:Argentine adventure movies Category:Movies directed by Armando Robles Godoy
title: No Stars in the Jungle
